Package models

Class State

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.State
  • public class State
extends Object
    Represents a state of a NFA. There are two possible kinds of transitions between states: symbol transitions and epsilon transitions. A state can have at most one symbol transition, or two epsilon transitions.
